item.title: How do i put in a clan system?
item.dc:creator: @yong_min yong min
item.description:
@yong_min wrote:

[quote=“Bladex0x, post:5, topic:275743”][quote author=yong min link=topic=364230.msg2765055#msg2765055 date=1240758215]

I searched for it using search bar but i didn’t find nothing

Interesting, I also did a search and found it straight away.

Edited my post and provided the link for you.
[/quote]I know this may sound retarded but where do i put “party.java”?[/quote]

Go into your server folder, then go to:

Src – Org – Rscdaemon – Server

Once in the server folder, create a new folder named “clan”. That is where your Party.java file will go.

If you was to open and read the Party.java file, you’d have seen:

package org.rscdaemon.server.clan;
[edit] sorry for me being so r-tarded about finding it I searched for "clan system" not "party system" my bad.

If you’d have just searched for “clan”, you’d have returned the correct search query.
